snippet.textDisplay:
I ❤ Bunny!
What's Bunny's story? How old is she? Where did you get her from? Why is she skittish, afraid of everything, what's that scar on her face from?
My kids and I love watching your videos. . you're so funny and your love for animals says a lot about your character. Which is a good thing. We are the same way with our 2 dog and 5 ferrets(they free roam).

My 6 year old said to me, "Mom, you know how people want to meet their favorite YouTubers? Well, I just want to meet their pets.. It would make me soo happy to meet Jenna's dogs! Do you think we could meet them one day? .. Meeting Jenna and Julian would be cool too.."

Jenna, if you read this.. Meet and greet with your dogs? ..we're in Wisconsin :(, so it probably won't ever happen for us, but I'm sure it would make your other subscribers very happy!

Merry Christmas and Happy New Year!
